               <cell width="284" pady="10">
                  <color r="255" g="255" b="255">Class: Mammals <i>(Mammalia)</i><br/>Order: Even-Toed Ungulates <i>(Artiodactyla)</i><br/>Family: Bovids <i>(Bovidae)</i><br/>Genus: <i>Addax</i><br/>Species: <i>nasomaculatus</i></color>
